The paper discusses privacy-preserving reporting techniques and algorithms, which are commonly studied in the computer security (cs.CR) and database (cs.DB) communities. The paper also evaluates the techniques using real-world datasets, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques, falling under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and computer vision (cs.CV).
